          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-john-sewel" title="Mr John Sewel">Lord Sewel</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I thank the noble Minister for his comments. I would hope to nudge him a little further at some stage, but I now beg leave to withdraw the amendment.</p><p>
            Amendment, by leave, withdrawn.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
