          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-harry-ewing" title="Mr Harry Ewing">Lord Ewing of Kirkford</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            On the basis of that assurance, I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
