          <p class='first-para'>
            It was read out at an earlier stage. I go through the Committee stage clause by clause. It is just the same as any other Committee stage. By convention, as I am sure the noble Lord will be aware, there are no Divisions. There are facilities but I go through the Bill clause by clause, amendment by amendment, and accordingly I put the
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_50gc' title='Col. 50GC &mdash; HL Deb 23 April 1996 vol 571 c50GC' name='column_50gc' href='#column_50gc' rel='bookmark'>50GC</a>
